(15, 1, '2014-07-29 13:06:51', '2014-07-29 12:06:51', '<strong>Localization</strong> is the process of translating a product into different languages or adapting a product for a specific country or regions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Software localization</strong>  is the adaptation of computer software for non-native environments, especially other nations and cultures. It is available for virtually any software application, platform and operating system. Product localization includes the graphical user interface, online help and documentation. Our expert-level engineering capabilities guarantee systematic QA, testing (both technical and linguistic) and debugging.\r\n\r\n<strong>Transcreation</strong> is a specific form of creative translation, resulting in a text linguistically, culturally and freely adapted for its intended audience.', 'Translation/Localization/Transcreation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'translation-localisation-transcreation', '', '', '2015-01-30 13:46:58', '2015-01-30 12:46:58', '', 13, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/?page_id=15', 1, 'page', '', 0),
(435, 1, '2014-12-08 23:13:18', '2014-12-08 22:13:18', 'Localization is the process of translating a product into different languages or adapting a product for a specific country or regions.\r\nSoftware localization  is the adaptation of computer software for non-native environments, especially other nations and cultures. It is available for virtually any software application, platform and operating system. Product localization includes the graphical user interface, online help and documentation. Our expert-level engineering capabilities guarantee systematic QA, testing (both technical and linguistic) and debugging.\r\nTranscreation is a specific form of creative translation, resulting in a text linguistically, culturally and freely adapted for its intended audience.', 'Translation / Localization / Transcreation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-08 23:13:18', '2014-12-08 22:13:18', '', 15, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
