(273, 1, '2015-01-29 10:14:12', '2015-01-29 09:14:12', 'We are a dynamic <strong>multilingual translation and localization company</strong>, supported by an experienced team and a network of native-speaking translators. Centrally headquartered in Brussels (Belgium), we currently work with international and high-tech companies from all over the world.\n\nSparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> is committed to providing premium quality multilingual translations in more than 80 languages.\n\nIf your business or services cross borders, or need to target local markets, all of your products and communications materials should accurately and strategically reflect the company behind them. At Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>, <strong>we care about your image</strong>. You can depend on us for the translation and localization of your brochures, user guides, softwares, marketing collaterals, videos and web content… And because we are professionals, just like you, <strong>we are dedicated to high-quality solutions</strong>.\n\nA high degree of personal attention to our "<strong>partner clients</strong>", combined with effective and efficient project management, make Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> a unique localization vendor.\n\nWe are currently active in the following sectors and keep expanding our capabilities to serve other markets as more and more clients decide to trust us with their translation needs and do not hesitate to <a title="Testimonials" href="http://sandrine-martinez.fr/sparklinglengua/home/en/testimonials/"><strong>let us know</strong></a> how much they appreciate our collaboration:\n<ul>\n	<li>Graphic Arts, Printing &amp; Publishing</li>\n	<li>Leisure and Tourism industries</li>\n	<li>Information &amp; Communication Technologies</li>\n	<li>RFID Technology</li>\n	<li>Industrial Automation &amp; Equipment</li>\n	<li>Consumer Products &amp; Services</li>\n	<li>Application Security &amp; Cloud computing</li>\n	<li>EU Environmental Legislation</li>\n	<li>Automotive Industry</li>\n	<li>Engineering &amp; Construction</li>\n	<li>Insurance &amp; Contracts</li>\n	<li>Finance</li>\n	<li>Medical/Health/Nutrition</li>\n	<li>Human Resources</li>\n</ul>\nSo let us become an <strong>extension of your services</strong> and… just relax!', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-29 10:14:12', '2015-01-29 09:14:12', '', 7, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/7-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(274, 1, '2014-07-29 17:33:16', '2014-07-29 16:33:16', 'We are a dynamic <strong>multilingual translation and localization company</strong>, supported by an experienced team and a network of native-speaking translators. Centrally headquartered in Brussels (Belgium), we currently work with international and high tech companies from all over the world.\r\n\r\nSparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> is committed to providing premium quality multilingual translations in more than 80 languages.\r\n\r\nIf your business or services cross borders, or need to target local markets, all of your products and communications materials should accurately and strategically reflect the company behind them. At Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>, <strong>we care about your image</strong>. You can depend on us for the translation and localization of your brochures, user guides, softwares, marketing collaterals, videos and web content… And because we are professionals, just like you, <strong>we are dedicated to high quality solutions</strong>.\r\n\r\nA high degree of personal attention to our ‘<strong>partner clients</strong>‘, combined with effective and efficient project management, make Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> a unique localization vendor.\r\n\r\nWe are currently active in the following sectors and keep expanding our capabilities to serve other markets, as more and more clients decide to trust us with their translation needs and do not hesitate to <strong>let us know</strong> (link to Testimonials) how much they appreciate our collaboration:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Graphic Arts, Printing &amp; Publishing</li>\r\n	<li>Leisure and Tourism industries</li>\r\n	<li>Information &amp; Communication Technologies</li>\r\n	<li>RFID Technology</li>\r\n	<li>Industrial Automation &amp; Equipment</li>\r\n	<li>Consumer Products &amp; Services</li>\r\n	<li>Application Security &amp; Cloud computing</li>\r\n	<li>EU Environmental Legislation</li>\r\n	<li>Automotive Industry</li>\r\n	<li>Engineering &amp; Construction</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance &amp; Contracts</li>\r\n	<li>Finance</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Health/Nutrition</li>\r\n	<li>Human Resources</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSo let us become an extension of your services and… just relax!', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-29 17:33:16', '2014-07-29 16:33:16', '', 7, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(275, 1, '2015-01-30 10:31:09', '2015-01-30 09:31:09', 'We <strong>care</strong> because we <strong>share</strong>\n<h2>Passion…</h2>\nYou don’t stay in the same industry for more than 15 years by coincidence. Ongoing learning allows us to keep developing our expertise, mastering for example the latest technology related to the translation industry. Most importantly, our relationships with the different stakeholders (clients, translators, etc.) are growing far beyond our expectations. It also feels great when we know clients are satisfied and they let us know. A passion for what you do is really what keeps you alive and kicking – and that’s the defining difference of Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>!\n<h2>We’ll find a way to make it work!</h2>\nWe are proactive optimists and we believe "<strong>where there’s a will, there’s a way</strong>". For that reason, we don’t automatically jump to the conclusion that a deadline is impossible. Our first goal is to make your deadline possible and we will make relentless efforts to reach the most optimal result/solution for you. We have long-standing relationships with partners who continue to surprise us about how fast they can deliver high-quality results on last-minute projects. We are proud to say that we have often helped our clients by turning "mission impossible" jobs into <strong>success stories</strong>.\n<h2>Beyond our projects are dedicated people</h2>\nThe biggest part of our daily work is interaction with people, so there is a strong emphasis on <strong>communication and psychology</strong>. Our experience has taught us that to truly succeed in the localization business, you also need patience and humor, along with a real desire to help and understand people. Sharing this commitment, our partners are flexible; they like their work and are proud of it.\n<h2>Quasi-colleagues…</h2>\nWe take a respectful, proactive approach to "partner" with our clients. A good translation and localization company is <strong>more than just a vendor, and</strong> here’s why: A top quality translation, transcreation or localization project begins with thorough preparation, wich involves  input from all players at the table (and their expectations), asking the right questions and sharing information. This foundation is built on trust and supported by excellent skills and tools, reliable response times and attentive service. No matter how complex a project is or how quickly it has to be done, it can be completed happily if translation partners agree "we are in this together and we all have the same goal". This approach has earned Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> much repeat business and <strong>sets us apart from others</strong>!', 'Our philosophy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-30 10:31:09', '2015-01-30 09:31:09', '', 11, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/11-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(301, 1, '2014-09-03 22:01:21', '2014-09-03 21:01:21', 'We <strong>care</strong> because we <strong>share</strong>\r\n<h2>Passion…</h2>\r\n“You don’t stay in the same industry for more than 15 years by coincidence. Ongoing learning allows us to keep developing our expertise, mastering for example the latest technology related to the translation industry. Most importantly, our relationships with the different stakeholders are growing far beyond our expectations. It also feels great when we know clients are satisfied and they let us know. A passion for what you do is really what keeps you alive and kicking – and that’s the defining difference about Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>!”\r\n<h2>We’ll find a way to make it work!</h2>\r\nWe are proactive optimists and believe “<strong>when there’s a will, there’s a way</strong>”. For that reason, we don’t automatically make the conclusion that a deadline is impossible. Our number one option is that your deadline is possible and we will make relentless efforts to reach the most optimal result/solution for you. We have long time relationships with partners who continue to surprise us about how fast they can deliver high-quality results on last-minute projects. We are proud to say that we have often helped our clients by turning ‘mission impossible’ jobs into <strong>success stories</strong>.\r\n<h2>Beyond our projects are dedicated people</h2>\r\nThe biggest part of our daily work is interaction with people, so there is a strong emphasis on <strong>communication and psychology</strong>. Our experience has taught us that to truly succeed in the localization business you also need patience and humor, along with a real desire to help and understand people. Sharing this commitment, our partners are flexible; they like their work and are proud of it.\r\n<h2>Almost colleagues…</h2>\r\nWe take a respectful, proactive approach to ‘partner’ with our clients. A good translation and localization company is <strong>more than just a vendor</strong> – here’s why! A top quality translation, transcreation or localization project begins with thorough preparation: input from all players at the table (and their expectations), asking the right questions and sharing information. This foundation is built on trust and supported by excellent skills and tools, reliable response times and attentive service. No matter how complex a project is or how quickly it has to be done, it can be completed happily if translation partners agree: we are in this together and we both have the same goal. This approach has earned Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> repeat-business and <strong>sets us apart from others</strong>!', 'Our philosophy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-03 22:01:21', '2014-09-03 21:01:21', '', 11, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(276, 1, '2014-07-29 18:40:07', '2014-07-29 17:40:07', 'We <strong>care</strong> because we <strong>share</strong>\r\n<h2>Passion…</h2>\r\n“You don’t stay in the same industry for more than 15 years by coincidence. Ongoing learning allows us to keep developing our expertise, mastering for example the latest technology related to the translation industry. Most importantly, our relationships with the different stakeholders are growing far beyond our expectations. It also feels great when we know clients are satisfied and they let us know. A passion for what you do is really what keeps you alive and kicking – and that’s the defining difference about Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>!”\r\n<h2>We’ll find a way to make it work!</h2>\r\nWe are proactive optimists and believe “<strong>when there’s a will, there’s a way</strong>”. For that reason, we don’t automatically make the conclusion that a deadline is impossible. Our number one option is that your deadline is possible and we will make relentless efforts to reach the most optimal result/solution for you. We have long time relationships with partners who continue to surprise us about how fast they can deliver high-quality results on last-minute projects. We are proud to say that we have often helped our clients by turning ‘mission impossible’ jobs into <strong>success stories</strong>.\r\n<h2>Beyond our projects are dedicated people</h2>\r\nThe biggest part of our daily work is interaction with people, so there is a strong emphasis on <strong>communication and psychology</strong>. Our experience has taught us that to truly succeed in the localization business you also need patience and humor, along with a real desire to help and understand people. Sharing this commitment, our partners are flexible; they like their work and are proud of it.\r\n<h2>Almost colleagues…</h2>\r\nWe take a respectful, proactive approach to ‘partner’ with our clients. A good translation and localization company is <strong>more than just a vendor</strong> – here’s why! A top quality translation, transcreation or localization project begins with thorough preparation: input from all players at the table (and their expectations), asking the right questions and sharing information. This foundation is built on trust and supported by excellent skills and tools, reliable response times and attentive service. No matter how complex a project is or how quickly it has to be done, it can be completed happily if translation partners agree: we are in this together and we both have the same goal. This approach has earned Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> repeat-business and <strong>sets us apart from others</strong>!\r\n<h2>Sparkling Lengua, your star network</h2>', 'Our phylosophy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-29 18:40:07', '2014-07-29 17:40:07', '', 11, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(277, 1, '2015-01-29 10:37:03', '2015-01-29 09:37:03', 'The first thing you need to know is that there is very little (actually, nothing comes to mind!) that we can''t do to meet all your translation needs. Any content you need translated (written text, video) we can process from scratch if you need us to. From file preparation and video transcription to the delivery of a brochure with a perfect layout or a subtitled video, you can rely on us, every step of the way - because we know what we''re doing!\n\nWe can assist you with single or multilingual translation (or transcreation) of your <strong>Marketing Collaterals</strong>, such as:\n<ul>\n	<li>Web pages</li>\n	<li>Brochures</li>\n	<li>Press releases</li>\n	<li>Datasheets</li>\n	<li>Mailers (HTML/OFTs,…)</li>\n	<li>Folders</li>\n	<li>Presentations</li>\n	<li>Videos</li>\n	<li>Banners</li>\n	<li>Etc.</li>\n</ul>\nWe also have strong expertise in <strong>Technical Documentation</strong>, such as:\n<ul>\n	<li>Software</li>\n	<li>Training guides</li>\n	<li>Manuals</li>\n	<li>User guides</li>\n	<li>User instructions</li>\n	<li>Quick reference sheets</li>\n	<li>Online helps</li>\n	<li>Database content</li>\n	<li>Etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Supported files formats</strong>: doc(x), xls(x), ppt(x), rtf, odt, html, xml (probably requiring some engineering preparation), indesign (inx, idml), tmx, sdlxliff, pdf (preparation needed), oft and more\n\nTo accurately translate all these different types of content, we rely on a trusted network of <strong>300 native speakers</strong> who are all experienced, professional translators. Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> can provide translation into more than <strong>80 languages</strong>:\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Western and Eastern European languages</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Scandinavian languages</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Asian languages</strong> (Simplified and Traditional Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Thai, Indonesian, )</li>\n	<li><strong>East and Middle-East languages</strong> (Arabic, Turkish, Hebrew, Farsi, …)</li>\n	<li><strong>American languages</strong> (American English, Canadian French, Brazilian Portuguese, Latin American Spanish and all South American Spanish dialects)</li>\n	<li><strong>Indian languages</strong> (Hindi, Gujarati, Nepali, Tamil, ...)</li>\n	<li><strong>African languages</strong> (Swahili, Afrikaans, ...)</li>\n	<li>And… from virtually <strong>any language</strong> into American, British and International English</li>\n</ul>\nWe are currently <strong>developing translation resources for Africa</strong>. This addresses our clients’ needs to tap into a large potential market, estimated to be 1 billion inhabitants by 2015.', 'Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-29 10:37:03', '2015-01-29 09:37:03', '', 13, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/13-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(278, 1, '2014-07-29 18:49:48', '2014-07-29 17:49:48', 'The first thing you need to know is that there is very little (actually, nothing comes to mind) we can''t do to answer all your translation needs. Any content you need translated (written text, video) we can process from scratch if you need us to. From file preparation and video transcription to the delivery of a brochure with a perfect layout or a subtitled video, you can trust us, every step of the way, because we know what we''re doing!\r\n\r\nWe can assist you with single or multilingual translation (or transcreation) of your <strong>Marketing Collaterals</strong>, such as:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Web pages</li>\r\n	<li>Brochures</li>\r\n	<li>Press releases</li>\r\n	<li>Datasheets</li>\r\n	<li>Mailers (HTML/OFTs,…)</li>\r\n	<li>Folders</li>\r\n	<li>Presentations</li>\r\n	<li>Videos</li>\r\n	<li>Banners</li>\r\n	<li>Etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe also have strong expertise in <strong>Technical Documentation</strong>, such as:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Software</li>\r\n	<li>Training guides</li>\r\n	<li>Manuals</li>\r\n	<li>User guides</li>\r\n	<li>User instructions</li>\r\n	<li>Quick reference sheets</li>\r\n	<li>Online helps</li>\r\n	<li>Database content</li>\r\n	<li>Etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Supported files formats</strong>: doc(x), xls(x), ppt(x), rtf, odt, html, xml (probably requiring some engineering preparation), indesign (inx, idml), tmx, sdlxliff, pdf (preparation needed), oft…\r\n\r\nTo accurately translate all these different types of contents, we rely on a trusted network of <strong>300 native-speakers</strong> who are experienced professional translators. Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> can provide translation into more than <strong>80 languages</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Western and Eastern European languages</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Scandinavian languages</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Asian languages</strong> (Simplified and Traditional Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Thai, Indonesian, …)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>East and Middle-East languages</strong> (Arabic, Turkish, Hebrew, Farsi, …)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>American languages</strong> (American English, Canadian French, Brazilian Portuguese, Latin American Spanish and all South American Spanish dialects)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Indian languages</strong> (Hindi, Gujarati, Nepali, Tamil, ...)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>African languages</strong> (Swahili, Afrikaans, ...)</li>\r\n	<li>And… from virtually <strong>any language</strong> into American, British and International English</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe are currently <strong>developing translation resources for Africa</strong>. This addresses our clients’ needs to tap into a large potential market, estimated to be 1 billion inhabitants by 2015.', 'Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-29 18:49:48', '2014-07-29 17:49:48', '', 13, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(279, 1, '2014-07-29 18:51:37', '2014-07-29 17:51:37', '<strong>Localization</strong> is the process of translating a product into different languages or adapting a product for a specific country or regions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Software localization</strong> is the adaptation of computer software for non-native environments, especially other nations and cultures.\r\n\r\n<strong>Software Localization</strong> is available for virtually any software application, platform and operating system. Product localization includes the graphical user interface, online help and documentation. Our expert-level engineering capabilities guarantee systematic QA, testing (both technical and linguistic) and debugging.\r\n\r\n<strong>Transcreation</strong> is a specific form of creative translation, resulting in a text linguistically, culturally and freely adapted for its intended audience.', 'Translation / Localisation / Transcreation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-29 18:51:37', '2014-07-29 17:51:37', '', 15, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(280, 1, '2014-12-08 23:13:16', '2014-12-08 22:13:16', 'Localization is the process of translating a product into different languages or adapting a product for a specific country or regions.\nSoftware localization  is the adaptation of computer software for non-native environments, especially other nations and cultures. It is available for virtually any software application, platform and operating system. Product localization includes the graphical user interface, online help and documentation. Our expert-level engineering capabilities guarantee systematic QA, testing (both technical and linguistic) and debugging.\nTranscreation is a specific form of creative translation, resulting in a text linguistically, culturally and freely adapted for its intended audience.', 'Translation / Localization / Transcreation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-12-08 23:13:16', '2014-12-08 22:13:16', '', 15, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/15-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(281, 1, '2014-07-29 18:54:16', '2014-07-29 17:54:16', '<h2>Localization :</h2>\r\nIs the process of translating a product into different languages or adapting a product for a specific country or regions.\r\n<h2>Software localization :</h2>\r\nIs the adaptation of computer software for non-native environments, especially other nations and cultures.\r\n<h2>Software Localization :</h2>\r\nIs available for virtually any software application, platform and operating system. Product localization includes the graphical user interface, online help and documentation. Our expert-level engineering capabilities guarantee systematic QA, testing (both technical and linguistic) and debugging.\r\n<h2>Transcreation :</h2>\r\nIs a specific form of creative translation, resulting in a text linguistically, culturally and freely adapted for its intended audience.', 'Translation / Localisation / Transcreation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-29 18:54:16', '2014-07-29 17:54:16', '', 15, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(282, 1, '2014-07-29 18:55:29', '2014-07-29 17:55:29', 'In this era of multichannel marketing, it’s not enough to be able to translate/localize pretty much any written content, in any format. It has now also become necessary to be able to localize any marketing material, including videos.\r\n\r\nAt Sparkling Lengua, we became aware of this early on and have since been offering subtitling/dubbing services. \r\n\r\nYour company posted a video in English on YouTube, which is a fantastic idea, but wouldn’t you like to share it in other languages with all your non-English speaking customers? Based on your needs, we can process it from scratch, transcribing its content and translating it before turning said translation into subtitles and inserting those directly into the video.\r\n\r\nWe can also help you if you’d rather have your video dubbed instead of subtitled, since we offer voice-over services as well.', 'Video Subtitling / Voice-over', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-29 18:55:29', '2014-07-29 17:55:29', '', 17, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(283, 1, '2014-07-29 18:56:11', '2014-07-29 17:56:11', 'Once the translations of your marketing collaterals or technical documentation are ready, we can immediately start placing the translated content into its original graphical environment. This is what we call Desktop Publishing.\r\nThe final deliverables will be the translated files ready to use in the original application format.\r\nOur Desktop Publishing team contributes years of expertise and is working with all the required software applications to translate and adapt (localize) your source documents into the requested target languages.\r\n\r\nSimply more: \r\nOur graphic team is also expert in visual communication design. Should you need a full service, from creation to final, ready to use multilingual products, we can also help!\r\n\r\nThe tools we use: Adobe Suite (InDesign, Illustrator, Photoshop, Acrobat Pro, FreeHand, FrameMaker, PageMaker), QuarkXPress, Microsoft Office Suite (PowerPoint, Word).', 'Desktop Publishing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-29 18:56:11', '2014-07-29 17:56:11', '', 19, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
