le in complement of the project management, as we come from different educational and professional backgrounds: translation, linguistics, desktop publishing, web design and creation, engineering, subtitling, marketing and management.</em>\r\n<h2>An extended translators’ network: more than 300 partners</h2>\r\nWe work with a strong infrastructure and network of effective partner translators to achieve total client satisfaction.\r\n\r\nAll our translators have a university degree in translation, industry-specific knowledge and translate only into their mother tongue. They are fully conversant with the trends, complexities and terminology of the high-tech industries.\r\n<h3>Sparkling <span style="color: #ff9900;">Lengua</span>’s mission is to offer you the very best of our experience in terms of efficiency, pricing, flexibility and networking.</h3>\r\n<h2>Translation Memories</h2>\r\nA Translation Memory is a database organized by language combinations (English/German for instance) and per client to store translations. Each translation is loaded into a database while being performed. This database is shared by the translators, enabling them to automatically recoup all matching or similar translations from previous or current projects.\r\n\r\nTranslation Memory technology delivers a number of <strong>significant benefits</strong> to the client:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Faster</strong> translation <strong>turn-around</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Higher stylistic, terminological and qualitative <strong>consistency</strong> across projects</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cost savings</strong> thanks to translated information recoup between different documents</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe Translation Memories are the client’s property and can be requested at any time.\r\n\r\nWe can also create and update customized glossaries for your specific market.\r\n<h2>Client validation</h2>\r\nIf the translation needs validation by an in-country reviewer prior to final delivery, we will be more than happy to liaise with your validators. It’s our belief that efficient and clear communication with your local subsidiaries enables us to collaborate towards a common goal: total satisfaction.\r\n\r\nThe validation is a process of tracing and documenting your feedback so that approved versions are later stored in the translation memories. Your in-country reviewer has the opportunity to review the translation versus the source text, to mark possible changes and add comments. This enables our translators to learn from the possible edits and take them into account for future projects.\r\n\r\n<strong>Outsource with confidence and let us manage the details!</strong>', 'Why us?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-22 01:25:34', '2014-12-22 00:25:34', '', 23, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(446, 1, '2014-12-22 01:29:31', '2014-12-22 00:29:31', 'We <strong>care</strong> because we <strong>share</strong>\r\n<h2>Passion…</h2>\r\n"You don’t stay in the same industry for more than 15 years by coincidence. Ongoing learning allows us to keep developing our expertise, mastering for example the latest technology related to the translation industry. Most importantly, our relationships with the different stakeholders are growing far beyond our expectations. It also feels great when we know clients are satisfied and they let us know. A passion for what you do is really what keeps you alive and kicking – and that’s the defining difference about Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>!"\r\n<h2>We’ll find a way to make it work!</h2>\r\nWe are proactive optimists and believe "<strong>when there’s a will, there’s a way</strong>". For that reason, we don’t automatically make the conclusion that a deadline is impossible. Our number one option is that your deadline is possible and we will make relentless efforts to reach the most optimal result/solution for you. We have long time relationships with partners who continue to surprise us about how fast they can deliver high-quality results on last-minute projects. We are proud to say that we have often helped our clients by turning "mission impossible" jobs into <strong>success stories</strong>.\r\n<h2>Beyond our projects are dedicated people</h2>\r\nThe biggest part of our daily work is interaction with people, so there is a strong emphasis on <strong>communication and psychology</strong>. Our experience has taught us that to truly succeed in the localization business you also need patience and humor, along with a real desire to help and understand people. Sharing this commitment, our partners are flexible; they like their work and are proud of it.\r\n<h2>Almost colleagues…</h2>\r\nWe take a respectful, proactive approach to "partner" with our clients. A good translation and localization company is <strong>more than just a vendor</strong> – here’s why! A top quality translation, transcreation or localization project begins with thorough preparation: input from all players at the table (and their expectations), asking the right questions and sharing information. This foundation is built on trust and supported by excellent skills and tools, reliable response times and attentive service. No matter how complex a project is or how quickly it has to be done, it can be completed happily if translation partners agree: we are in this together and we all have the same goal. This approach has earned Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> repeat-business and <strong>sets us apart from others</strong>!', 'Our philosophy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-22 01:29:31', '2014-12-22 00:29:31', '', 11, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(447, 1, '2014-12-22 01:34:23', '2014-12-22 00:34:23', '<strong>Localization</strong> is the process of translating a product into different languages or adapting a product for a specific country or regions.\r\n\r\n<strong>Software localization</strong>  is the adaptation of computer software for non-native environments, especially other nations and cultures. It is available for virtually any software application, platform and operating system. Product localization includes the graphical user interface, online help and documentation. Our expert-level engineering capabilities guarantee systematic QA, testing (both technical and linguistic) and debugging.\r\n\r\n<strong>Transcreation</strong> is a specific form of creative translation, resulting in a text linguistically, culturally and freely adapted for its intended audience.', 'Translation/Localization/Transcreation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-22 01:34:23', '2014-12-22 00:34:23', '', 15, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(448, 1, '2014-12-22 01:34:34', '2014-12-22 00:34:34', 'In this era of multichannel marketing, it’s not enough to be able to translate/localize pretty much any written content, in any format. It has now also become necessary to be able to localize any marketing material, including videos.\r\n\r\nAt Sparkling Lengua, we became aware of this early on and have since been offering subtitling/dubbing services.\r\n\r\nYour company posted a video in English on YouTube, which is a fantastic idea, but wouldn’t you like to share it in other languages with all your non-English speaking customers? Based on your needs, we can process it from scratch, transcribing its content and translating it before turning said translation into subtitles and inserting those directly into the video.\r\n\r\nWe can also help you if you’d rather have your video dubbed instead of subtitled, since we offer voice-over services as well.\r\n\r\n<strong>Video examples:</strong>\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfMLg3c01P8\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfVU43DfV-E\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfMLg3c01P8">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfMLg3c01P8</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfVU43DfV-E">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfVU43DfV-E</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Video Subtitling/Voice&#x2011;over (Dubbing)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-22 01:34:34', '2014-12-22 00:34:34', '', 17, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(449, 1, '2014-12-22 01:34:46', '2014-12-22 00:34:46', 'It is easy to say ‘I have the best products, technologies or software on the market’. It’s a lot more convincing to let your clients say it for you!\r\n\r\nSparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>’s network of skilled copywriters expertly craft compelling success stories and client testimonials, which will open the door to new markets and allow to target prospective clients. This content can then be translated/localized in more than 80 different languages to accurately convey your product messaging and corporate branding. We offer a <strong>360-degree approach for your communication needs</strong>!', 'Copywriting/Creation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-22 01:34:46', '2014-12-22 00:34:46', '', 21, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/21-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(450, 1, '2014-12-22 01:36:51', '2014-12-22 00:36:51', 'Once the translations of your marketing collaterals or technical documentation are ready, we can immediately start placing the translated content into its original graphical environment. This is what we call Desktop Publishing.\r\nThe final deliverables will be <strong>the translated files ready to use in the original application format</strong>.\r\nOur Desktop Publishing team contributes years of expertise and is working with all the required software applications to translate and adapt (localize) your source documents into the requested target languages.\r\n\r\n<strong>Simply more: </strong>\r\nOur graphic team is also expert in <strong>visual communication design</strong>. Should you need a full service, from creation to final, ready to use multilingual products, we can also help!\r\n\r\n<strong>The tools we use :</strong>\r\nAdobe Suite (InDesign, Illustrator, Photoshop, Acrobat Pro, FreeHand, FrameMaker, PageMaker), QuarkXPress, Microsoft Office Suite (PowerPoint, Word)', 'Desktop Publishing (DTP)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-22 01:36:51', '2014-12-22 00:36:51', '', 19, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
