(462, 1, '2015-01-18 23:25:31', '2015-01-18 22:25:31', 'Once the translations of your marketing collaterals or technical documentation are ready, we can immediately start placing the translated content into its original graphical environment. This is what we call Desktop Publishing.\r\nThe final deliverables will be <strong>the translated files ready to use in the original application format</strong>.\r\nOur Desktop Publishing team contributes years of expertise and is working with all the required software applications to translate and adapt (localize) your source documents into the requested target languages.\r\n\r\n<strong>Simply more: </strong>\r\nOur graphic team is also expert in <strong>visual communication design</strong>. Should you need a full service, from creation to final, ready to use multilingual products, we can also help!\r\n\r\n<strong>The tools we use:</strong>\r\nAdobe Suite (InDesign, Illustrator, Photoshop, Acrobat Pro, FreeHand, FrameMaker, PageMaker), QuarkXPress, Microsoft Office Suite (PowerPoint, Word)\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sandrine-martinez.fr/sparklinglengua/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/a0d0a0d219bbd76ed4135267ebc54770.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-455" src="http://sandrine-martinez.fr/sparklinglengua/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/a0d0a0d219bbd76ed4135267ebc54770-194x300.jpg" alt="a0d0a0d219bbd76ed4135267ebc54770" width="194" height="300" /></a><a href="http://sandrine-martinez.fr/sparklinglengua/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/a0d0a0d219bbd76ed4135267ebc547701.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-454" src="http://sandrine-martinez.fr/sparklinglengua/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/a0d0a0d219bbd76ed4135267ebc547701-194x300.jpg" alt="a0d0a0d219bbd76ed4135267ebc54770" width="194" height="300" /></a><a href="http://sandrine-martinez.fr/sparklinglengua/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/a0d0a0d219bbd76ed4135267ebc54770.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-453 size-medium" src="http://sandrine-martinez.fr/sparklinglengua/wp-content/uplo