(531, 1, '2015-01-29 10:16:42', '2015-01-29 09:16:42', 'We are a dynamic <strong>multilingual translation and localization company</strong>, supported by an experienced team and a network of native-speaking translators. Centrally headquartered in Brussels (Belgium), we currently work with international and high-tech companies from all over the world.\r\n\r\nSparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> is committed to providing premium quality multilingual translations in more than 80 languages.\r\n\r\nIf your business or services cross borders, or need to target local markets, all of your products and communications materials should accurately and strategically reflect the company behind them. At Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>, <strong>we care about your image</strong>. You can depend on us for the translation and localization of your brochures, user guides, softwares, marketing collaterals, videos and web content… And because we are professionals, just like you, <strong>we are dedicated to high-quality solutions</strong>.\r\n\r\nA high degree of personal attention to our "<strong>partner clients</strong>", combined with effective and efficient project management, make Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> a unique localization vendor.\r\n\r\nWe are currently active in the following sectors and keep expanding our capabilities to serve other markets as more and more clients decide to trust us with their translation needs and do not hesitate to <a title="Testimonials" href="http://sandrine-martinez.fr/sparklinglengua/home/en/testimonials/"><strong>let us know</strong></a> how much they appreciate our collaboration:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Graphic Arts, Printing &amp; Publishing</li>\r\n	<li>Leisure and Tourism industries</li>\r\n	<li>Information &amp; Communication Technologies</li>\r\n	<li>RFID Technology</li>\r\n	<li>Industrial Automation &amp; Equipment</li>\r\n	<li>Consumer Products &amp; Services</li>\r\n	<li>Application Security &amp; Cloud computing</li>\r\n	<li>EU Environmental Legislation</li>\r\n	<li>Automotive Industry</li>\r\n	<li>Engineering &amp; Construction</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance &amp; Contracts</li>\r\n	<li>Finance</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Health/Nutrition</li>\r\n	<li>Human Resources</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSo let us become an <strong>extension of your services</strong> and… just relax!', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-29 10:16:42', '2015-01-29 09:16:42', '', 7, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(532, 1, '2015-01-29 10:33:17', '2015-01-29 09:33:17', 'We <strong>care</strong> because we <strong>share</strong>\r\n<h2>Passion…</h2>\r\n"You don’t stay in the same industry for more than 15 years by coincidence. Ongoing learning allows us to keep developing our expertise, mastering for example the latest technology related to the translation industry. Most importantly, our relationships with the different stakeholders are growing far beyond our expectations. It also feels great when we know clients are satisfied and they let us know. A passion for what you do is really what keeps you alive and kicking – and that’s the defining difference of Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>!"\r\n<h2>We’ll find a way to make it work!</h2>\r\nWe are proactive optimists and we believe "<strong>where there’s a will, there’s a way</strong>". For that reason, we don’t automatically jump to the conclusion that a deadline is impossible. Our first goal is to make your deadline possible and we will make relentless efforts to reach the most optimal result/solution for you. We have long-standing relationships with partners who continue to surprise us about how fast they can deliver high-quality results on last-minute projects. We are proud to say that we have often helped our clients by turning "mission impossible" jobs into <strong>success stories</strong>.\r\n<h2>Beyond our projects are dedicated people</h2>\r\nThe biggest part of our daily work is interaction with people, so there is a strong emphasis on <strong>communication and psychology</strong>. Our experience has taught us that to truly succeed in the localization business, you also need patience and humor, along with a real desire to help and understand people. Sharing this commitment, our partners are flexible; they like their work and are proud of it.\r\n<h2>Quasi-colleagues…</h2>\r\nWe take a respectful, proactive approach to "partner" with our clients. A good translation and localization company is <strong>more than just a vendor, and</strong> here’s why: A top quality translation, transcreation or localization project begins with thorough preparation, wich involves  input from all players at the table (and their expectations), asking the right questions and sharing information. This foundation is built on trust and supported by excellent skills and tools, reliable response times and attentive service. No matter how complex a project is or how quickly it has to be done, it can be completed happily if translation partners agree "we are in this together and we all have the same goal". This approach has earned Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> much repeat business and <strong>sets us apart from others</strong>!', 'Our philosophy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-29 10:33:17', '2015-01-29 09:33:17', '', 11, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(534, 1, '2015-01-29 10:41:48', '2015-01-29 09:41:48', 'Once the translations of your marketing collaterals or technical documentation are ready, we can immediately start placing the translated content into its original graphical environment. This is what we call Desktop Publishing.\r\nThe final deliverables will be <strong>the translated files ready to use in the original application format</strong>.\r\nOur Desktop Publishing team contributes years of expertise and works with all the required software applications to translate and adapt (localize) your source documents into the requested target languages.\r\n\r\n<strong>Simply more: </strong>\r\nOur graphic team is also expert in <strong>visual communication design</strong>. Should you need a full service, from creation to final, ready-to-use multilingual products, we can also help!\r\n\r\n<strong>The tools we use:</strong>\r\nAdobe Suite (InDesign, Illustrator, Photoshop, Acrobat Pro, FreeHand, FrameMaker, PageMaker), QuarkXPress, Microsoft Office Suite (PowerPoint, Word)', 'Desktop Publishing (DTP)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-29 10:41:48', '2015-01-29 09:41:48', '', 19, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(535, 1, '2015-01-29 10:43:28', '2015-01-29 09:43:28', 'It''s easy to say "I have the best products, technologies or software on the market". But it’s a lot more convincing when your clients say it for you!\n\nSparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>’s network of skilled copywriters expertly craft compelling success stories and client testimonials, which will open the door to new markets and allow to target prospective clients. This content can then be translated/localized in more than 80 different languages to accurately convey your product messaging and corporate branding. We offer a <strong>360-degree approach for your communication needs</strong>!', 'Copywriting/Creation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '21-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-29 10:43:28', '2015-01-29 09:43:28', '', 21, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/21-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(536, 1, '2015-01-29 10:44:26', '2015-01-29 09:44:26', 'It''s easy to say "I have the best products, technologies or software on the market". But it’s a lot more convincing when your clients say it for you!\r\n\r\nSparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>’s network of skilled copywriters expertly craft compelling success stories and client testimonials, which will open the door to new markets and allow you to target a wider spectrum of potential clients. This content can then be translated/localized in more than 80 different languages to accurately convey your product messaging and corporate branding. We offer a <strong>360-degree approach for your communication needs</strong>!', 'Copywriting/Creation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-29 10:44:26', '2015-01-29 09:44:26', '', 21, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/21-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(783, 1, '2015-02-26 16:19:49', '2015-02-26 15:19:49', 'Uw doel is ons doel en we bewegen hemel en aarde om dit te realiseren\r\n<h2>PASSIE…</h2>\r\nHet is geen toeval dat ik al meer dan vijftien jaar actief ben in deze sector. Het is een passie. We leren voortdurend bij zodat expertise blijft groeien. Zo zorgen we er bijvoorbeeld voor dat we de nieuwste vertaaltechnologie beheersen. Ook belangrijk is onze goede relatie met de verschillende stakeholders (klanten, vertalers enz.). Die wordt bovendien steeds sterker, zo sterk zelfs dat het onze verwachtingen ver overtreft. Het is bovendien een fantastisch gevoel dat klanten ons laten weten dat ze tevreden zijn. Passie hebben voor wat je doet, zorgt dat je elke dag opnieuw met veel zin ertegenaan gaat. En hiermee onderscheidt Sparkling <strong>Lengua </strong>zich van de rest!\r\n<h2>WE VERZETTEN BERGEN OM U TE HELPEN</h2>\r\nWe zijn proactieve optimisten en geloven in het motto "<strong>waar een wil is, is een weg</strong>". Daarom zult u van ons nooit meteen te horen krijgen dat een deadline te krap is. We gaan er steeds eerst vanuit dat de deadline die u stelt, haalbaar is. We stellen alles in het werk om u het beste resultaat en de beste oplossing te bieden. Onze partners zijn mensen met wie we al lang samenwerken. Het blijft ons verbazen binnen welke strakke deadlines zij resultaten van hoge kwaliteit kunnen leveren voor lastminuteprojecten. We zijn er trots op dat we klanten al vaak uit de nood hebben geholpen door opdrachten die een "mission impossible" leken, tot een <strong>succesverhaal </strong>te maken.\r\n<h2>EÉN EN AL TOEWIJDING ACHTER DE SCHERMEN</h2>\r\nHet grootste deel van ons dagelijkse werk bestaat uit interactie met mensen. De nadruk ligt in grote mate op <strong>communicatie en psychologie</strong>. Om echt succesvol te zijn in de lokalisatiesector, zo hebben we geleerd, heb je een dosis geduld en humor nodig. Ook moet je gedreven zijn en je goed kunnen verplaatsen in klanten om inzicht te krijgen in hun wensen. Onze partners delen deze overtuiging en stellen zich soepel op; ze houden van hun werk en zijn trots op de resultaten.\r\n<h2>NET COLLEGA''S…</h2>\r\nWe werken op een respectvolle en proactieve manier samen met onze klanten. We beschouwen hen als partners. Een goed vertaal- en lokalisatiebedrijf is <strong>veel meer dan alleen maar een leverancier</strong>. In welk opzicht? Het succes van een vertaal-, transcreatie- of lokalisatieproject staat of valt met grondige voorbereiding: input verzamelen van alle stakeholders (en de verwachtingen definiëren), de juiste vragen stellen en informatie delen. Centraal hierbij staan vertrouwen, uitstekende vaardigheden en tools, hoge reactiesnelheid en service van topkwaliteit. Ongeacht de complexiteit of de deadline van uw project, vertrouw ons maar. Wij maken er een succes van door te zorgen voor optimale betrokkenheid bij alle stakeholders en duidelijke doelstellingen. Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> <strong>onderscheidt zich van de concurrentie </strong>met deze aanpak. En met succes, want onze klanten blijven terugkeren!', 'Onze filosofie', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '232-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-26 16:19:49', '2015-02-26 15:19:49', '', 232, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/232-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(537, 1, '2015-01-29 10:50:51', '2015-01-29 09:50:51', '<h2>Highly transparent &amp; competitive pricing</h2>\r\nOur pricing is highly competitive, being positioned between <strong>the standard market rates for freelancers</strong> and <strong>translation agencies</strong>.\r\n\r\nOur price quotations are <strong>straightforward</strong> and <strong>transparent</strong>. We take care to detail the price per language, per word and per translation recoup category. Thanks to the <strong>translation memories,</strong> you may not be charged for the full source-text word count as you may be able to benefit from pre-existing text that has already been fully or partially translated. We take the translation recoup into account in our quotations and "translate" the level of your savings into €.\r\n<h2>First-class Project Management!</h2>\r\nWe are your <strong>direct interface</strong> in the management of all Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>’s projects.\r\nYou can depend on us to coordinate the different resources, prepare translatable files and gather all reference materials, develop and maintain schedules and optimally allocate the appropriate Certified Partner. We consistently follow up on the progress of the on-going projects, communicate detailed status reports and deliver the final translated/localized products as per your initial deadlines.\r\n<h2>Our experience is your advantage!</h2>\r\nThe management team at Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> contributes more than 15 years of senior Project Management expertise, with in-house corporate experience. This has given us a real-life perspective of the pros and the cons, the "must-do" and the "take-care-to-avoid" processes for successfully managing translation projects. There is no time to lose when it comes to urgent projects. Our project management approach is both agile and methodical – meeting your deadline without delays, high prices or surcharges.\r\n\r\nThe Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> team is truly rich in diversity; as French writer Bernard Werber postulated, 1+1=3, the collective talent exceeds the sum of the individual talents. We all have very specific skills that we bring to the table to enrich the project management process since we all come from different educational and professional backgrounds: translation, linguistics, marketing, sales, desktop publishing, graphical creations and web design.\r\n<h2>An extensive network of translators: more than 300 partners</h2>\r\nWe work with a strong infrastructure and network of effective partner translators to achieve total client satisfaction.\r\n\r\nAll our translators have a university degree in translation, industry-specific knowledge and translate only into their mother tongue. They are fully conversant with the trends, complexities and terminology of the high-tech industries.\r\n<h3>Sparkling <span style="color: #ff9900;">Lengua</span>’s mission is to offer you the very best of our experience in terms of efficiency, pricing, flexibility and networking.</h3>\r\n<h2>Translation Memories</h2>\r\nA Translation Memory is a database organized by language combinations (English/German for instance) and per client to store translations. Each translation is loaded into a database while being performed. This database is shared by the translators, enabling them to automatically recoup all matching or similar translations from previous or current projects.\r\n\r\nTranslation Memory technology delivers a number of <strong>significant benefits</strong> to the client:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Faster</strong> translation <strong>turn-around</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Higher stylistic, terminological and qualitative <strong>consistency</strong> across projects</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cost savings</strong> thanks to translated information recoup between different documents</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe Translation Memories are the client’s property and can be requested at any time.\r\n\r\nWe can also create and update customized glossaries for your specific market.\r\n<h2>Client validation</h2>\r\nIf the translation needs validation by an in-country reviewer prior to final delivery, we will be more than happy to liaise with your validators. It’s our belief that efficient and clear communication with your local subsidiaries enables us to collaborate towards a common goal: total satisfaction.\r\n\r\nThe validation is a process of tracing and documenting your feedback so that approved versions are later stored in the translation memories. Your in-country reviewer has the opportunity to review the translation versus the source text, to mark possible changes and add comments. This enables our translators to learn from the possible edits and take them into account for future projects.\r\n\r\n<strong>Outsource with confidence and let us manage the details!</strong>', 'Why us?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-29 10:50:51', '2015-01-29 09:50:51', '', 23, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
