(568, 1, '2015-01-30 10:26:53', '2015-01-30 09:26:53', 'We are a dynamic <strong>multilingual translation and localization company</strong>, supported by an experienced team and a network of native-speaking translators. Centrally headquartered in Brussels (Belgium), we currently work with international and high-tech companies from all over the world.\r\n\r\nSparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> is committed to providing premium quality multilingual translations in more than 80 languages.\r\n\r\nIf your business or services cross borders and therefore need to target local markets, all of your products and communications materials should accurately and strategically reflect the company behind them. At Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>, <strong>we care about your image</strong>. You can depend on us for the translation and localization of your brochures, user guides, softwares, marketing collaterals, videos and web content… And because we are professionals, just like you, <strong>we are dedicated to high-quality solutions</strong>.\r\n\r\nA high degree of personal attention to our "<strong>partner clients</strong>", combined with effective and efficient project management, make Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> a unique localization vendor.\r\n\r\nWe are currently active in the following sectors and keep expanding our capabilities to serve other markets as more and more clients decide to trust us with their translation needs and do not hesitate to <a title="Testimonials" href="http://www.sparklinglengua.com/home/en/testimonials/"><strong>let us know</strong></a> how much they appreciate our collaboration:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Graphic Arts, Printing &amp; Publishing</li>\r\n	<li>Leisure and Tourism industries</li>\r\n	<li>Information &amp; Communication Technologies</li>\r\n	<li>RFID Technology</li>\r\n	<li>Industrial Automation &amp; Equipment</li>\r\n	<li>Consumer Products &amp; Services</li>\r\n	<li>Application Security &amp; Cloud computing</li>\r\n	<li>EU Environmental Legislation</li>\r\n	<li>Automotive Industry</li>\r\n	<li>Engineering &amp; Construction</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance &amp; Contracts</li>\r\n	<li>Finance</li>\r\n	<li>Medical/Health/Nutrition</li>\r\n	<li>Human Resources</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSo let us become an <strong>extension of your services</strong> and… just relax!', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-30 10:26:53', '2015-01-30 09:26:53', '', 7, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(569, 1, '2015-01-30 10:31:22', '2015-01-30 09:31:22', 'We <strong>care</strong> because we <strong>share</strong>\r\n<h2>Passion…</h2>\r\nYou don’t stay in the same industry for more than 15 years by coincidence. Ongoing learning allows us to keep developing our expertise, mastering for example the latest technology related to the translation industry. Most importantly, our relationships with the different stakeholders (clients, translators, etc.) are growing far beyond our expectations. It also feels great when we know clients are satisfied and they let us know. A passion for what you do is really what keeps you alive and kicking – and that’s the defining difference of Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>!\r\n<h2>We’ll find a way to make it work!</h2>\r\nWe are proactive optimists and we believe "<strong>where there’s a will, there’s a way</strong>". For that reason, we don’t automatically jump to the conclusion that a deadline is impossible. Our first goal is to make your deadline possible and we will make relentless efforts to reach the most optimal result/solution for you. We have long-standing relationships with partners who continue to surprise us about how fast they can deliver high-quality results on last-minute projects. We are proud to say that we have often helped our clients by turning "mission impossible" jobs into <strong>success stories</strong>.\r\n<h2>Beyond our projects are dedicated people</h2>\r\nThe biggest part of our daily work is interaction with people, so there is a strong emphasis on <strong>communication and psychology</strong>. Our experience has taught us that to truly succeed in the localization business, you also need patience and humor, along with a real desire to help and understand people. Sharing this commitment, our partners are flexible; they like their work and are proud of it.\r\n<h2>Quasi-colleagues…</h2>\r\nWe take a respectful, proactive approach to "partner" with our clients. A good translation and localization company is <strong>more than just a vendor</strong>, and here’s why: A top quality translation, transcreation or localization project begins with thorough preparation, wich involves  input from all players at the table (and their expectations), asking the right questions and sharing information. This foundation is built on trust and supported by excellent skills and tools, reliable response times and attentive service. No matter how complex a project is or how quickly it has to be done, it can be completed happily if translation partners agree "we are in this together and we all have the same goal". This approach has earned Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> much repeat business and <strong>sets us apart from others</strong>!', 'Our philosophy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-30 10:31:22', '2015-01-30 09:31:22', '', 11, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(570, 1, '2015-01-30 10:32:46', '2015-01-30 09:32:46', 'The first thing you need to know is that there is very little (actually nothing comes to mind!) that we can''t do to meet all your translation needs. Any content you need translated (written text, video) we can process from scratch if you need us to. From file preparation and video transcription to the delivery of a brochure with a perfect layout or a subtitled video, you can rely on us, every step of the way - because we know what we''re doing!\r\n\r\nWe can assist you with single or multilingual translation (or transcreation) of your <strong>Marketing Collaterals</strong>, such as:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Web pages</li>\r\n	<li>Brochures</li>\r\n	<li>Press releases</li>\r\n	<li>Datasheets</li>\r\n	<li>Mailers (HTML/OFTs,…)</li>\r\n	<li>Folders</li>\r\n	<li>Presentations</li>\r\n	<li>Videos</li>\r\n	<li>Banners</li>\r\n	<li>Etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe also have strong expertise in <strong>Technical Documentation</strong>, such as:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Software</li>\r\n	<li>Training guides</li>\r\n	<li>Manuals</li>\r\n	<li>User guides</li>\r\n	<li>User instructions</li>\r\n	<li>Quick reference sheets</li>\r\n	<li>Online helps</li>\r\n	<li>Database content</li>\r\n	<li>Etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Supported files formats</strong>: doc(x), xls(x), ppt(x), rtf, odt, html, xml (probably requiring some engineering preparation), inDesign (inx, idml), tmx, sdlxliff, pdf (preparation needed), oft and more\r\n\r\nTo accurately translate all these different types of content, we rely on a trusted network of <strong>300 native speakers</strong> who are all experienced, professional translators. Sparkling <strong>Lengua</strong> can provide translation into more than <strong>80 languages</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Western and Eastern European languages</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Scandinavian languages</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Asian languages</strong> (Simplified and Traditional Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Thai, Indonesian, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>East and Middle-East languages</strong> (Arabic, Turkish, Hebrew, Farsi, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>American languages</strong> (American English, Canadian French, Brazilian Portuguese, Latin American Spanish and all South American Spanish dialects)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Indian languages</strong> (Hindi, Gujarati, Nepali, Tamil, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>African languages</strong> (Swahili, Afrikaans, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>And… from virtually <strong>any language</strong> into American, British and International English</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe are currently <strong>developing translation resources for Africa</strong>.', 'Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-30 10:32:46', '2015-01-30 09:32:46', '', 13, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(571, 1, '2015-01-30 10:33:52', '2015-01-30 09:33:52', 'It''s easy to say, "I have the best products, technologies or software on the market". But it’s a lot more convincing when your clients say it for you!\r\n\r\nSparkling <strong>Lengua</strong>’s network of skilled copywriters expertly craft compelling success stories and client testimonials, which will open the door to new markets and allow you to target a wider spectrum of potential clients. This content can then be translated/localized in more than 80 different languages to accurately convey your product messaging and corporate branding. We offer a <strong>360-degree approach for your communication needs</strong>!', 'Copywriting/Creation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-30 10:33:52', '2015-01-30 09:33:52', '', 21, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/21-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(575, 1, '2015-01-30 10:59:44', '2015-01-30 09:59:44', 'We all know "a picture is worth a thousand words". Well in this case, we thought we would let our work and results speak for themselves by showing you some examples of what we can do.\r\n\r\n<strong>Reference projects:\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfMLg3c01P8\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfVU43DfV-E\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>', 'We did it!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-30 10:59:44', '2015-01-30 09:59:44', '', 25, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
