ou have the right to file a complaint with the Commission for the Protection of Privacy, which will become the Data Protection Authority from 25 May 2018 onwards (<a href="https://www.privacycommission.be/">https://www.privacycommission.be/</a>).', 'Our privacy and data protection policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '894-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-21 14:49:13', '2018-05-21 13:49:13', '', 894, 'http://www.sparklinglengua.com/894-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
